title: Interview with A True Crime Psychic Medium - Part Two
description:
We pick up right where we left off with special guest Psychic Medium Ginette Matacia Lucas who's been contacted by various major news networks about her insight into prolific unsolved murder investigations.

Want more paranormal episodes? Follow our new podcast 'Paranormal Fears' on any podcast app or Apple Podcasts.
